high_descs: Take a left and then a right into the bedroom and go to the brown dresser.
Pick up the back mango on the dresser.
Leave the room and go to the kitchen straight ahead and go to the microwave.
Place the mango in the microwave turn it on and take it out.
Turn around to the sink behind you.
Place the mango on the counter near the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved mango on the counter near the sink close to the fridge.

high_descs: walk left and forward into the bedroom and approach the dresser in the corner
Pick up the mango closest to the wall from the dresser
Exit the bedroom and walk forward into the kitchen then face the microwave
Heat the mango in the microwave then remove it
Turn around to face towards the kitchen sink
Put the mango on the edge of the counter left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mango on the countertop

high_descs: Head left to enter the bedroom and reach the side table.
Pick up the mango from the side table.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and turn right to head to the kitchen to reach the microwave.
Heat the mango in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to reach the sink.
Put the mango in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mango in the sink.
